Thanks for downloading this map.

A map for Counter Strike: Source

Creator: MrCraftersMan

One of the best tutoriols on making a map with Source SDK: 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?IblzeE-4M&v=1VyoitE17Wc

How to download:

1.go to you'r steamapps folder (C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps)

2.open common => Counter-Strike Source => cstrike => maps and drag in gg_maze in to the maps folder.
